<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span style="color:#006d98">حدَّث عن:</span> يوسف بن موسى القطان.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span style="color:#006d98">روى عنه:</span> الطَّبراني.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#950000">"تاريخ بغداد"</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٨/ ٢٤٦)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
